Title: LN2 Welcome Back Ice Cream
Book Description: For the opening session of Liquid Nitrogen Ice Cream- we tell you the ingredients on hand and we make fun and tasty flavors together.  Alternative ingredients available; we can make some non-dairy or sugar-free!

Title: LN2 After Hours I Ice Cream
Book Description: Some ice creams / sorbets may be made with alcohol for this event.  Only legal drinking age attendees allowed.  IDs will be checked.

Title: LN2 Guest Flavors Ice Cream
Book Description: Ice cream flavors celebrating the 2016 guests of honor and featured guests (e.g.- Radchai tea ice cream)

Title: LN2 After Hours II Ice Cream
Book Description: Some ice creams / sorbets may be made with alcohol for this event.  Only legal drinking age attendees allowed.  IDs will be checked.

Title: LN2 Sunday Brunch Ice Cream
Book Description: Ice cream made with liquid nitrogen- for a Sunday brunch!  Flavors will include orange- coffee- and Captain Crunch or some other sugary breakfast treat. Alternative ingredients available; we can make some non-dairy or sugar-free!
